Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在武道館辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,武道館？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧 就這種自發性的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想讓那些努力的孩子們站上夢想的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,既然要實現 就要實現最棒的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺 你還有精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我過得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,已經換季更衣 秋天的氣氛漸漸濃厚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天我真的很開心 時間轉瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我和明日香她們去了游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,還去了夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟Popipa親密交流了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好幸福呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說亞子和Roselia的大家去了海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她們在海邊的音樂工作室裡強化合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow的成員在圖書館裡寫了暑假作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡好涼爽 能待上一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說Hello,Happy World也去了很涼快的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,反而Pastel*Palettes好像去了更熱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 RAISE A SUILEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那是來參觀了Popipa主辦演唱會的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,現在好像很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你們全毀了 給我做好覺悟啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然那之後我就沒關注了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那個“全毀了”到底是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,毀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毀（壓扁）？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,壓扁壓扁 揉一揉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,壓扁壓扁 揉一揉呀揉一揉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,揉一揉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要弄成糰子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是糰子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人一串哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真對不起 她們那麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 畢竟外面那麼冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在的時候歡迎隨時過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好糯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,給 沙綾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲 心情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 你是在期待今天的倉庫練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒猜中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有咲你起得那麼早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好久沒在倉庫裡一起見面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也不至於那麼久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今天放學之後也沒學生會的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們家今天也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,里美今天也不用補課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一開始就能過去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 怎麼樣 要做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都說要練習了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有哪的窗戶沒關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把小火爐拿去有咲家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小火爐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,放在哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 你要跟到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,E班在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,多惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這幫人又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,里美 有咲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這邊取暖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa還真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy！Lucky！Smile…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,心！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello Happy還真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,請路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那位我覺得還挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,RAISE A SUILEN可是最強的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,半桶水的吉他手可是No thank you的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是難道要一直靠外援的吉他手開演唱會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不是一直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果不是只為我奏響的吉他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能把Roselia毀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前就想問你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“毀了”是要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒在想什麼危險的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,當然！我是要讓他們心服口服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,具體要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經找好了最適合的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 在找到最棒的吉他手之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,面試要一直繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就專心訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在 CHU²大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要肉乾是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No！給我把下一個面試選手叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那位就是最後一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,倉練 倉練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你麵包買太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子餓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得只買一隻太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“只”？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說米歇爾麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這是秋季的新品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道LOCK在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,去分她一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等會要嚐嚐米歇爾麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有壞人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,BanG Dream！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,武道館！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,說是武道館哦 武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 武道館！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 這下熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這下真熱鬧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里奈 這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這是附近的Live House一起策劃的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們努力拿下武道館了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害啊 蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然必須得拼進決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧 武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 幹嘛沒人配合我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,友希那 友希那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不出場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們要準備Future World Fes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,現在分不了這個心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,亞子 你對武道館有興趣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亞子 那是搖滾的聖地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那出場吧 一起參加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Galaxy也是預選賽場地之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是剛剛聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,武道館 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要根據觀眾的投票贏得高排位才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有多少樂隊要參加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲你之前也說過想去武道館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,追尋同一個夢想 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得哪天能上武道館也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那才不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“這個”？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說 大家有共同的夢想真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…也沒有啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道能不能進入決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起努力也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲也來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa Pipopa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipapa Pipopa！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,目標武道館！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK也要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK也加入Popipa 一起登上武道館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要我加入Popipa什麼的 不敢當啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你對武道館沒興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不是沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太煩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 讓你們費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為我沒有樂隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明明你從春天開始就一直在募集成員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,照這樣下去還能不能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK的吉他明明彈得那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭那次真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要不還是要加入Popipa吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你找到樂隊成員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa的各位真溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡Popipa了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,說錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 你是益木嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我是第一次看你穿校服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是高中生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我不是這個意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在吵什麼架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 益木 你這樣坐著裙子要皺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是在這附近的學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是從幼兒園到大學一應俱全 名叫白雪學院的名媛學校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是名媛 但她又整天泡在父親開的Live House裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是真正的深閨大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1147,970)}箱入り娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,深閨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是指Live House的包廂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我去打一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在樂隊還挺順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫RAISE A SUILEN嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,名字太長了 叫RAS就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 是那個“揉糰子”的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet！Excellent！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你最喜歡Roselia了對吧 CHU²
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,才不！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你一直在看Roselia的影片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我這是在研究對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,確實她們是精彩出色的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是越強越有打敗的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要用自己的音樂問鼎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要什麼製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,湊友希那 竟然敢小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,俗話說愛之深責之切…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你妨礙著我了 快走開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會妨礙你了 請讓我待在這
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,肉乾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes PAREO！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭… 新的影片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大家請嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,武道館演唱會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你太著急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,表象訓練很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 我完全想像不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟武道館就像做夢一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 Bang！Dream！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呃… 我還想再見姐姐一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,里美 沙綾！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,逮捕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,BanG Dream 是這意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾各位休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝各位的聲援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,私闖民宅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是從正門進來 讓您奶奶帶路到這的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉沒有事先預約
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1210,970)}Appointment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Appoi？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這是會面的客套話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這回是什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要那麼警戒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是來給您把這個帶過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,並… 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,您能記住我 不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再次自我介紹 我是CHU²的鍵盤手女僕 PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日六花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,7月17日出生 巨蟹座 A血型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,岐阜縣出身 從春天開始住在這家澡堂裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨要打掃浴室 白天上學 晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是您的請帖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,請帖？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會把你帶上一個全新的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'party也會到場的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,RAS的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,單獨演唱會？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,觀眾好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,之前都夠多了 這次還更多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沙綾她們馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你們來了啊 就兩個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不 五個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,難道Popipa收到請帖了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 Roselia也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟對方來請了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她們自稱女子樂隊大時代的新領袖 這點我也很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,女子樂隊大時代的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,新領袖？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,里美和沙綾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在看物販呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK 你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我差點被人流淹沒 多惠學姐救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一桿釣起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我不願意來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但難得對方邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子 在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,RAS RAS RAS…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 超乎我想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,吉他是事先錄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但就算這樣 演奏還是很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,果然好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,多惠學姐 你曾經在那上面演奏的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,KING Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在唱安可曲之前先來一個精彩的告知哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的樂隊 RAISE A SUILEN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,將要參加BanG Dream！女子樂隊挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼那麼 重要的還在後頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在BanG Dream裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把Roselia和Popipa給親手毀掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,糰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為了實現這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,六花·朝日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要將你收入麾下
